gard to the journey towards socialism.\u201d\n\nOn the occasion, the NCP Chairman said that they were advancing to the new journey towards economic development for further flourishing the federal democratic republic.\n\n\u201cThere are obviously challenges at this time. But, the communist party itself has the power to counter such problems and challenges,\u201d he argued.\n\nWelcoming those leaders and cadres in the NCP, he assured them of appropriate responsibilities on the basis of the new entrants\u2019 qualification, capacity and experience.","title":"NCP has responsibility to make socialism-oriented state, Prachanda says - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/12/148416/","video":[]}
